# file for https://github.com/charmbracelet/vhs video demo
Set Shell nu
Set TypingSpeed 500ms
Output demo.gif
Type pj
Sleep 500ms
Enter

Sleep 500ms
Up 1
Sleep 300ms
Up 1
Sleep 500ms
Up 1
Sleep 500ms
Enter

Sleep 1s
Type pwd
Enter

Sleep 2s

Type "pj "
Tab

Sleep 2s
Backspace

Type "-"
Tab

Sleep 3s